<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TechPoint | Catálogo Completo</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .card-img-top { height: 200px; object-fit: cover; }
        .card { transition: transform 0.3s; }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark sticky-top shadow">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">TECH<span class="text-primary">POINT</span></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMenu">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navMenu">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto text-uppercase small">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="/produto">Produtos</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/fotos">Galeria</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/contato">Contato</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="bg-white py-5 border-bottom mb-5">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1 class="fw-bold">Nosso Catálogo</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">Equipamentos de alta performance para quem não aceita menos que o melhor.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container mb-5">
        <div class="row g-4">
            
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591488320449-011701bb6704?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" class="card-img-top" alt="GPU">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Placa de Vídeo RX 7900</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted flex-grow-1">Performance máxima para Ray Tracing e resoluções 4K.</p>
                        <h6 class="text-primary fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">R$ 5.200,00</h6>
                        <a href="/detalhes" class="btn btn-dark w-100 rounded-pill">Ver Detalhes</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544244015-0df4b3ffc6b0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" class="card-img-top" alt="Tablet">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Tablet Pro X12</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted flex-grow-1">Tela OLED 120Hz e processador de última geração.</p>
                        <h6 class="text-primary fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">R$ 3.800,00</h6>
                        <a href="/detalhes2" class="btn btn-dark w-100 rounded-pill">Ver Detalhes</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511467687858-23d96c32e4ae?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" class="card-img-top" alt="Teclado">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">Teclado Mecânico RGB</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted flex-grow-1">Switches Blue para maior precisão tátil e sonora.</p>
                        <h6 class="text-primary fw-bold fs-5 mb-3">R$ 450,00</h6>
                        <a href="/detalhes3" class="btn btn-dark w-100 rounded-pill">Ver Detalhes</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
